  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2021-02-25",
    "date": "2021-04-06T21:01:49Z",
    "text": "Pandemic Heroes Compensation Act of 2021\n\nThis bill allows essential workers and their family members to file claims and receive compensation for harm or death suffered as a result of COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019).\n\nA Special Master appointed by the Department of Justice must review claims submitted and determine if a claimant\u00a0is eligible for compensation, the extent of the harm to the claimant, and the amount of compensation to be awarded."
  },
